name: Long Beaded Colorblock Necklace - Black & White - Silk and Sterling Silver
description:
Bold color-blocking makes this necklace so modern & unique - a real head-turner!

Eight inches of black & white beads (black jasper & white snow quartz) are accented by small Czech teal glass beads. It measures 28" in length and is strung on a 100% silk cord. It's long enough to slip over your head, but I've included a Sterling Silver clasp. All metal components are Sterling Silver.

name: Long Beaded Wood & Yellow Bead Necklace - Silk and Sterling Silver
description:
Very fresh & light for spring and summer! 

Eight inches of lightweight oval wooden beads are accented by small yellow glass beads. The necklace measures 28" in length and is strung on a 100% silk cord. It's long enough to slip over your head, but I've included a Sterling Silver clasp. All metal components are Sterling Silver.

name: Tiny Pearl Necklace - Silk Cord, Pearls, and Sterling Silver
description:
Such a unique and modern way to wear pearls!

This dainty necklace features 1.5" of tiny white freshwater pearls strung onto a light pink 100% silk cord. The pearls are hand-knotted into place. It measures 16"in length and fastens with a Sterling Silver lobster clasp. The raw-edge of the silk at the clasp adds to the "organic" feel.

All metal components are made of Sterling Silver.

name: Gay Rights Bracelet for The Ally Coalition - Silk & Metal Hand-Stamped Wrap Bracelet - Blue
description:
I'm proud to be partnering with The Ally Coalition - founded by the band FUN. and designer Rachel Antonoff - to donate the profits from every bracelet sold directly to their charity to support LGBTQ equality. $15.00 from each sale will go to The Ally Coalition, and the rest simply pays for the supplies.

Show your support by telling the world that you're an Ally. The bracelet features an aluminum tag that has been hand-stamped with the word "ALLY." The tag is then curved slightly to fit the wrist. The 100% silk ribbon is strung through the tag and is then easily wrapped around your wrist - no clasp needed! Simply tie or tuck the ends under when you get to the end.

ALSO AVAILABLE IN BLACK. This listing is for a blue "denim" silk color (inspired by Fun.). 

Please note that the word ALLY is stamped by hand and therefore will differ from the example in the photos. Not one is alike, and not one is "perfect" - just like all of us!

------------------------------------------------------

QUESTION: WHERE DOES THE ALLY COALITION DONATE MONEY?

(from Jack Antonoff of fun.): many different places – we donate a bunch of money to high school GSA’s all over the country to help them operate and continue to do the work they do. we support bigger organizations like the trevor project, glaad, revel and riot and the HRC.

but lately we’ve turned a lot of our focus to homeless LGBTQ youth. a lot of the money coming in now will go to support places like the ruth ellis center in detroit or the oasis center in nashville. these are places where LGBTQ youth who have been kicked out and living on the street can go and live / get their lives back on track. they are amazing facilities.

For more information on The Ally Coalition, please visit:
http://www.theallycoalition.org/

name: Ombre Blue Bead & Silk Cord Necklace
description:
Itty bitty glass beads in shades of blue are strung in an ombre effect on a delicate gray silk cord. 

The necklace measures nearly 17" in length, and the beaded portion is 4 inches. It fastens with all Sterling Silver components, including a lobster clasp.

name: Pink Painted Rectangle Pendant & Gold Fill Chain Color-Blocked Necklace
description:
This necklace features a sturdy gold-plated pewter rectangle that has been hand-painted pink and topped with a satin varnish. So simple, and so modern! 

The pendant is a gold-plated pewter, but the rest of the necklace is 14k gold-fill... don't skimp on quality! This will help ensure that your chain is unlikely to tarnish. The clasp is entirely 14k gold-fill as well.

It measures approximately 17" in length and fastens with a lobster claw clasp. The rectangle pendant measures approximately 9mm x 30mm (or .54 inches x 1.18 inches). The 4th photo shows the necklace in white, just to give an idea of dimension & size.

name: White Painted Circle Color Block Earrings with 14k Gold Fill Earwires
description:
These earrings feature sturdy gold-plated pewter circles that have been hand-painted white and topped with a satin varnish. So simple, and so modern! The circles are approximately 20mm in diameter (0.79 inches).

The circles are a gold-plated pewter, but the earwires are14k gold-fill... don't skimp on quality!

name: GOLDEN NUGGET Red Silk & Gold Vermeil Nugget Necklace
description:
This combination of golden nuggets & silk cord feels so organic & natural!

Ten 22k gold vermeil nuggets are strung onto a red 100% silk cord and hand-knotted into place. It measures 16" in length and fastens with a gold-filled lobster clasp. The raw-edge of the silk at the clasp adds to the "organic" feel.

The "nuggets" are 22k Gold Vermeil (gold over sterling silver), and all other metal components are made of Gold Fill.

name: LULU - Pink Freshwater Pearl & Silk Cord Necklace
description:
So sweet! Fifteen tiny real freshwater pearls in a beautiful pink/peach color hang so delicately along a light pink silk cord necklace. This necklace is so light and airy, and a great contemporary way to wear pearls.

The necklace measures 21" in length and fastens with all Sterling Silver components, including a lobster clasp.

name: Gemstone Necklace with Green Onyx, Apatite, and Sterling Silver
description:
Gemstone Necklace with Green Onyx, Apatite, and Sterling Silver Gemstone Necklace with Green Onyx, Apatite, and Sterling Silver Gemstone Necklace with Green Onyx, Apatite, and Sterling Silver Gemstone Necklace with Green Onyx, Apatite, and Sterling Silver 


So unique and rich! A row of bright blue apatite rondelles and a single green onyx briolette are the focal on this necklace. The chain is Sterling Silver. It measures approximately 17" (so that it sits right at the collarbone), and fastens with all Sterling Silver components, including a lobster clasp.

name: CINQ - Circle Gold Fill Minimalist Chain Necklace
description:
You'll get so much wear out of this necklace - it goes with just about everything!

Five little 14k Gold Filled circles hang so delicately at your neckline, and are accented on both sides with a small vermeil nugget. The chain is 14k gold-fill, and measures approximately 17" in length. 

The clasp is made of 14k gold-fill components, including a nice lobster clasp, and is accented again with two more vermeil nuggets.

name: Long Pearl Necklace - Pearl & Silk Cord Hand Knotted Station Necklace
description:
The perfect accessory - trendy yet very classic! 

This pearl station necklace features real ivory freshwater pearls that are hand-knotted, in duos, on black 100% silk cord. The silk is delicate yet durable, and makes this necklace oh-so-light! The silk is black, so if worn against a dark color it makes the pearls POP!

The necklace is extra long - measuring 42

name: SKYSCRAPER
description:
Delicate, yet strong.

A half inch of tiny gold vermeil nuggets hang on a 1.5" sterling silver chain.  Accented with another vermeil nugget, the earrings hang on a sterling silver french earwire.

name: AUTUMN - Copper Leaf & Gold Chain Necklace
description:
This will be your new favorite necklace for fall! 

This necklace features three inches of tiny copper-plated leaves that are strung on a 14k gold-filled chain. The leaves are so detailed, and drape so delicately. Accented on each side of the copper leaf chain is a tiny gold vermeil nugget.

The total length of the necklace is approximately 17". It closes with a gold-filled lobster clasp and large loop to make fastening easy.

name: DEW DROP - Clear Quartz & 14k Gold Fill Onion Briolette Earrings
description: The perfect wardrobe staple! These feature clear quartz "onion" shaped briolettes that are carefully wire-wrapped using 14k gold fill wire onto pretty circular 14k gold fill earwires.

name: HEX - Pink Mystic Quartz Hexagon & 14k Gold Fill Gemstone Necklace
description:
When I saw these gemstones, I just could not pass them up!

This necklace features a beautiful stone you don't see every day - a pink mystic quartz gemstone in a gorgeous hexagon shape. It has been carefully wire-wrapped with 14k gold-filled wire onto a delicate 14k gold-fill chain. 

The necklace measures approximately 17" in length and fastens with 14k gold-fill components, including a lobster claw clasp, and vermeil nuggets.

name: ICE - Blue Apatite & Blue Quartz Sterling Silver Cube Gemstone Earrings
description:
These earrings feature a faceted quartz gemstone cube iin a very light blue color- it's nearly clear. The cube is accented by a small apatite gem in a beautiful vibrant turquoise color. They are wire-wrapped with Sterling Silver wire onto Sterling Silver earwires.

They measure a little over 1" in length including the earwire, and the dangle itself (no earwire) is just around a half inch in length.

MATERIALS:
- Sterling Silver
- Ice Quartz
- Apatite

name: BASIL - Green Amethyst, Green Onyx & Gold Fill Cube Gemstone Drop Earrings
description:
The green-on-green look of this gemstone combination is so fresh! 

A faceted light green amethyst (prasiolite) gemstone cube is accented by a small grass-green onyx gem. They hang on 14k gold-filled earwires.

They measure a little over 1" in length including the earwire, and the dangle itself (no earwire) is just around a half inch in length.
